                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18220417-168-off876 t18220417-168-cd877"></join>, forty pounds of lead, value 10 s., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18220417-168-victim1579" type="victimName">
                           John 
